graph TB
    Start[User Request:<br/>GET /api/v1/m/projects/123] --> JWT[JWT Token Present?]
    
    JWT -->|No| Error1[‚ùå 401 Unauthorized<br/>No token provided]
    JWT -->|Yes| Extract[Extract from JWT:<br/>user_id: uuid-456<br/>services: M, Dashboard]
    
    Extract --> ServiceCheck{Is 'M' in<br/>services array?}
    ServiceCheck -->|No| Error2[‚ùå 403 Forbidden<br/>No access to service M]
    ServiceCheck -->|Yes| AuthPass[‚úÖ Authentication PASSED]
    
    AuthPass --> RBACStart[RBAC: Check API-Level Permission]
    
    RBACStart --> CacheCheck1{Check Redis<br/>user:uuid-456:permissions:M}
    CacheCheck1 -->|Cache Hit| PermArray[Get cached permissions:<br/>view_projects ‚úì<br/>create_leads ‚úì<br/>edit_projects ‚úì]
    CacheCheck1 -->|Cache Miss| QueryRoles[Query Database:<br/>What roles does user have?]
    
    QueryRoles --> RoleResult[User Roles:<br/>‚Ä¢ sales_rep role_id=4<br/>‚Ä¢ team_lead role_id=3<br/>  scope: project_id=789]
    
    RoleResult --> QueryPerms[Query Permissions:<br/>SELECT DISTINCT p.permission_name<br/>FROM user_roles ur<br/>JOIN role_permissions rp<br/>  ON ur.role_id = rp.role_id<br/>JOIN permissions p<br/>  ON rp.permission_id = p.permission_id<br/>WHERE ur.user_id = uuid-456]
    
    QueryPerms --> PermResult[Combined Permissions:<br/>‚Ä¢ view_projects<br/>‚Ä¢ create_leads<br/>‚Ä¢ edit_leads<br/>‚Ä¢ edit_projects<br/>‚Ä¢ assign_leads]
    
    PermResult --> CacheStore[Store in Redis<br/>TTL: 10 minutes]
    CacheStore --> PermArray
    
    PermArray --> CheckRequired{Has<br/>'view_projects'<br/>permission?}
    
    CheckRequired -->|No| Error3[‚ùå 403 Permission Denied<br/>Missing: view_projects]
    CheckRequired -->|Yes| RBACPass[‚úÖ RBAC PASSED<br/>User can call this API]
    
    RBACPass --> ABACStart[ABAC: Check Resource-Level Permission]
    
    ABACStart --> CacheCheck2{Check Redis<br/>user:uuid-456:resource:project:123}
    CacheCheck2 -->|Cache Hit| PermLevel[Get permission level:<br/>editor]
    CacheCheck2 -->|Cache Miss| QueryResource[Query Database:<br/>SELECT permission_level<br/>FROM resource_permissions<br/>WHERE user_id = uuid-456<br/>  AND resource_type = 'project'<br/>  AND resource_id = '123'<br/>  AND expires_at > NOW]
    
    QueryResource --> ResourceResult{User has<br/>access to<br/>project 123?}
    
    ResourceResult -->|No rows| Error4[‚ùå 403 Access Denied<br/>No access to this project]
    ResourceResult -->|Yes| GetLevel[permission_level:<br/>editor]
    
    GetLevel --> CacheResource[Store in Redis<br/>Key: user:uuid-456:resource:project:123<br/>Value: editor<br/>TTL: 5 minutes]
    CacheResource --> PermLevel
    
    PermLevel --> ABACPass[‚úÖ ABAC PASSED<br/>User can access project 123]
    
    ABACPass --> FetchData[Fetch Project Data:<br/>SELECT * FROM projects<br/>WHERE project_id = 123]
    
    FetchData --> ProjectData[Raw Project Data:<br/>‚Ä¢ project_id: 123<br/>‚Ä¢ name: Q4 Campaign<br/>‚Ä¢ description: ...<br/>‚Ä¢ budget: 50000 üí∞<br/>‚Ä¢ internal_notes: ... üìù<br/>‚Ä¢ team_members: ...<br/>‚Ä¢ created_at: ...]
    
    ProjectData --> FieldFilter[Apply Field-Level Filtering<br/>Based on permission_level = editor]
    
    FieldFilter --> FilterLogic{Permission<br/>Level?}
    
    FilterLogic -->|owner| ShowAll[Show ALL fields:<br/>‚Ä¢ All data visible<br/>‚Ä¢ No restrictions]
    FilterLogic -->|editor| HideSome[Hide sensitive fields:<br/>‚ùå budget<br/>‚ùå internal_notes<br/>‚ùå profit_margin<br/>‚úÖ Everything else visible]
    FilterLogic -->|viewer| HideMany[Show basic fields only:<br/>‚úÖ project_id<br/>‚úÖ name<br/>‚úÖ description<br/>‚úÖ status<br/>‚úÖ created_at<br/>‚ùå All other fields]
    
    ShowAll --> FinalData
    HideSome --> FinalData[Filtered Project Data]
    HideMany --> FinalData
    
    FinalData --> Response[200 OK Response:<br/>{<br/>  project_id: 123,<br/>  name: Q4 Campaign,<br/>  description: ...,<br/>  team_members: ...,<br/>  created_at: ...,<br/>  user_permission_level: editor<br/>}]
    
    Response --> AuditLog[Log in Audit Trail:<br/>‚Ä¢ user_id<br/>‚Ä¢ action: view_project<br/>‚Ä¢ resource_id: 123<br/>‚Ä¢ timestamp<br/>‚Ä¢ result: success]
    
    AuditLog --> End[‚úÖ Request Complete]
    
    Error1 --> End
    Error2 --> End
    Error3 --> End
    Error4 --> End

